-- Citigroup says plans sale of Turkish retail banking business
-- 
-- Wed Dec 5, 2012 11:34am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/12/05/us-citi-turkey-idUSBRE8B40UR20121205

 

 ISTANBUL  (Reuters) - Citigroup is evaluating options for the sale of its retail banking business in Turkey and will focus on corporate and commercial banking in the country going forward, its Turkish unit said on Wednesday. 
 "As part of its global strategy ... Citi has started to evaluate options for the sale of its retail banking operations in Turkey," Citigroup Turkey said in a statement. (Reporting by Asli Kandemir; Writing by  Nick Tattersall )